{
  "texts": [
    "However, this approach estimates delay solely based on CPU power without considering communications related factors.Shapley Value-based Methods: In [165], a two-phase framework incentivizing edge servers in a collaborative cloudedge-device setting was proposed.",
    "It leverages Shapley Value (SV) to distribute rewards based on edge server contributions.",
    "However, it does not incentivize data-contributing devices.",
    "SVbased methods [190] can assess contributions by FL clients, but often incur high computation costs.",
    "To address this issue, [166] introduced the Contribution Index (CI) based on SVs."
  ]
}